prodNameC: 常盈性荷爾蒙結合球蛋白免疫放射試劑組
ingredientsDesc:
SHBG Standard A/Sample Diluent:
One bottle, 55 mL, labelled A, containing 0 nmol/L of SHBG in a protein-based buffer with sodium azide as a preservative.
SHBG Standards B-F:
Five vials, labelled B-F, containing concentrations of approximately 5, 25, 75, 150 and 300 nmol/L of SHBG (human) in a protein-based buffer with sodium azide as a preservative.
Anti-SHBG [I-125] Reagent:
One bottle, 22 mL, containing <10 μCi (370 kBq) of [I-125]-labeled anti-SHBG in a protein-based buffer with sodium azide as a preservative. 
Anti-SHBG-Coated Tubes:
Four bags, each containing 25 plastic tubes, with anti-SHBG immunoglobulin immobilized to the inside wall of each tube.
SHBG Controls:
Two vials, Level I and Level II, containing low and high concentrations of SHBG in a protein-based buffer with sodium azide as a preservative.
applicantName: 常盈實業股份有限公司
applicantAddr: 台北市北投區永興路一段49號
efficacy: 利用放射性免疫定量方法檢測血清中的性荷爾蒙結合球蛋白。
